### 智慧教室核心接口冒烟测试
### 使用 VS Code REST Client 按顺序执行；修改示例 ID 后再执行写操作。

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@aiUrl = http://localhost:5000
@internalToken = replace-with-ai-internal-token
@userId = 2
@streamDbId = 1
@streamId = classroom_01
@alertId = 1
@zoneId = 1
@ruleId = 1
@studentId = 1

### 1. 服务健康
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/health

### 2. 管理员登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 登录后令牌
@jwt = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 3. 当前用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/info
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 4. 用户列表（仅管理员）
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 5. 修改其他用户角色（仅管理员）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/role
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "teacher"
}

### 6. 已启用视频源
GET {{baseUrl}}/streams/enabled
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 7. 新增视频源（仅管理员）
POST {{baseUrl}}/streams
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stream_id": "classroom_test",
  "stream_name": "测试教室摄像头",
  "rtmp_url": "rtmp://localhost:9090/live/classroom_test",
  "remark": "接口联调"
}

### 8. 视频源状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/streams/{{streamId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 9. 告警列表（查询参数按 Controller 使用 camelCase）
GET {{baseUrl}}/alerts?streamId={{streamId}}&status=unhandled&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 10. 处理告警
PUT {{baseUrl}}/alerts/{{alertId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "handled",
  "handler_id": 1,
  "remark": "已人工复核"
}

### 11. 告警统计
GET {{baseUrl}}/alert-stats
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 12. 当前视频源区域
GET {{baseUrl}}/zones?streamId={{streamId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 13. 新增区域（coordinates 是 JSON 字符串）
POST {{baseUrl}}/zones
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stream_id": "{{streamId}}",
  "zone_name": "测试危险区",
  "zone_type": "danger",
  "coordinates": "[{\"x\":0.10,\"y\":0.10},{\"x\":0.45,\"y\":0.10},{\"x\":0.45,\"y\":0.50},{\"x\":0.10,\"y\":0.50}]",
  "threshold_seconds": 3,
  "safe_distance": 0.05
}

### 14. 修改区域名称、类型和阈值
PUT {{baseUrl}}/zones/{{zoneId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "zone_name": "测试座位区",
  "zone_type": "seat",
  "threshold_seconds": 5,
  "safe_distance": 0,
  "enabled": true
}

### 15. 启停区域
PUT {{baseUrl}}/zones/{{zoneId}}/toggle?enabled=true
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 16. 规则列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/rules
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 17. 启停规则
PUT {{baseUrl}}/rules/{{ruleId}}/toggle?enabled=true
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 18. 告警评分配置
GET {{baseUrl}}/score-config
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 19. 人员列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/students?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 20. 新增人员（仅管理员）
POST {{baseUrl}}/students
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_no": "TEST-001",
  "name": "测试人员",
  "class_name": "联调班"
}

### 21. 注册人脸（替换为真实 Base64）
POST {{baseUrl}}/students/{{studentId}}/face
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image": "<base64-image>"
}

### 22. 录像列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/recordings?streamId={{streamId}}&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 23. 操作日志（仅管理员）
GET {{baseUrl}}/operation-logs?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### 24. AI 模型状态
GET {{aiUrl}}/model/status

### 25. AI 事件
GET {{aiUrl}}/analysis/events?stream_id={{streamId}}&limit=20

### 26. 通知 AI 重新加载区域配置
POST {{aiUrl}}/config/reload
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stream_id": "{{streamId}}",
  "reload_items": ["zones"]
}

### 27. AI 告警写入 SpringBoot（内部接口，event_id 幂等）
POST {{baseUrl}}/alerts/ai
X-Internal-Token: {{internalToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "http-test-event-001",
  "stream_id": "{{streamId}}",
  "alert_type": "danger_zone_intrusion",
  "alert_name": "危险区域入侵",
  "level": "high",
  "confidence": 0.91,
  "occurred_at": "2026-07-12T12:00:00+08:00",
  "duration_seconds": 2.4,
  "target_info": {
    "bbox": [120, 80, 220, 300]
  },
  "zone_id": {{zoneId}},
  "snapshot_path": "/snapshots/http-test-event-001.jpg"
}

### 28. 删除测试区域（谨慎执行）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/zones/{{zoneId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
